==古生态学==
[[File:Stegouros_tail.jpg|left]]
[[正模标本|正模标本]]骨骼收集于南极{{le|雪丘岛组|Snow Hill Island Formation}}伽马段（Gamma Member）底部约{{cvt|90|m|ft}}处。<ref name="olivero2012">{{cite journal |author=Olivero, E.B. |year=2012 |title=Sedimentary cycles, ammonite diversity and palaeoenvironmental changes in the Upper Cretaceous Marambio Group, Antarctica |journal=Cretaceous Research |volume=34 |pages=348–366 |doi=10.1016/j.cretres.2011.11.015}}</ref>该[[地层|层段]]沉积于[[海洋|浅海]][[环境|环境]]中，还保存着[[鲨鱼|鲨鱼]]牙齿、[[沧龙类|沧龙类]]的[[海怪龙|南极拉库玛龙]]、[[菊石|菊石]]、[[双壳类|双壳类]]及[[腹足类|腹足类]]等海洋生物化石。菊石等[[标准化石|标准化石]]显示这些岩石沉积于大约7400至7000万年前的[[晚白垩世|晚白垩世]][[坎帕阶|坎帕阶]]晚期。<ref name="oliveroetal1991"/>尽管南极甲龙发现于海洋沉积物中，但与所有甲龙类一样生活在陆地上。海洋沉积物中亦发现其它甲龙类，可能是尸体被冲入大海的结果。<ref name="horner1979">{{cite journal |author=Horner, J.R. |year=1979 |title=Upper Cretaceous dinosaurs from the Bearpaw Shale (Marine) of southcentral Montana, with a checklist of Upper Cretaceous dinosaur remains from marine sediments in North America |journal=Journal of Paleontology |volume=53 |issue=3 |pages=566–577}}</ref><ref name="carpenteretal1995">{{cite journal |doi=10.1080/02724634.1995.10011230 |author1=Carpenter, K. |author2=Dilkes, D. |author3=Weishampel, D.B. |year=1995 |title=The dinosaurs of the Niobrara Chalk Formation (upper Cretaceous, Kansas) |journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology |volume=15 |issue=2 |pages=275–297 }}</ref><ref name="lee1996">{{cite journal |doi=10.1080/02724634.1996.10011311 |author=Lee Y.-N. |year=1996 |title=A new nodosaurid ankylosaur (Dinosauria: Ornithischia) from the Paw Paw Formation (Late Albian) of Texas |journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology |volume=16 |issue=2 |pages=232–245 }}</ref>

尽管{{le|南极洲地质|Geology of Antarctica#Mesozoic|白垩纪的南极洲}}位于南[[极区|极区]]，但这段时期的地球[[气候|气候]]更为温暖，因此该大陆不会结冰。像南极甲龙这样的动物可能生活在[[针叶林|针叶林]]甚至[[落叶阔叶林|落叶阔叶林]]中。尽管气温较高，但在冬天黑暗仍然会降临，就像今天的高[[纬度|纬度]]地区一样。<ref name="huber1998">{{cite journal |author=Huber, B.T. |year=1998 |title=Tropical Paradise at the Cretaceous Poles? |journal=Science |volume=282 |issue=5397 |pages=2199–2200 |doi=10.1126/science.282.5397.2199 |s2cid=129523803 }}</ref>包括詹姆斯罗斯岛在内的南极半岛在此期间一直与[[南美|南美]]相连，使两洲之间的动物群得以[[扩散_(生态学)|交流]]。事实上，近期发现的智利副甲龙类[[覆尾龙|覆尾龙]]表明这些恐龙也居住在南美洲。<ref>{{cite journal |title=Armoured dinosaurs of the Southern Hemisphere |journal=Nature |date=1 December 2021 |pages=d41586–021–03572-6 |doi=10.1038/d41586-021-03572-6 |pmid=34853419 |s2cid=244830406 }}</ref>

